io.micronaut.annotation.processing

Class ServiceDescriptionProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.annotation.processing.AbstractProcessor
      • io.micronaut.annotation.processing.ServiceDescriptionProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor

    @SupportedOptions(value={"micronaut.processing.incremental","micronaut.processing.annotations"})
public class ServiceDescriptionProcessor
extends AbstractProcessor
    A separate aggregating annotation processor responsible for creating META-INF/services entries.
    Since:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    graemerocher
